It's not strange... Life is like a leaf swaying on the water's
surface, only able to be carried away. And yet, everyone...
rushes to live in search of happiness...

...Don't look at me like that. I just tried to say something
profound and failed, that's all.

I built this bridge when I was young. If you use it, I would be
very happy.
